version_description: This tubs includes both chords and tubs so the player can match the song more accurately and the tubs would still be very easy.
Based off album version – capo on 3rd fret, simplified chords a bit.
This is the only version with the lyrics and chords over them for easy follow-along playing :).
Standard tuning version of the song.

song_name: Livin My Life Like A Country Song
